<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Dashboard - Terve</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f7fa;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .navbar {
      background: #003580;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .navbar-brand {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .navbar-user {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .logout-btn {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .welcome {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .welcome h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .welcome p { color: #666; }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }
    .card-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .card h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .card p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .card-link {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #003580;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .card-link:hover { background: #004494; }
    .level-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #e3f2fd;
      color: #1976d2;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">üá´üáÆ Terve</a>
    <div class="navbar-user">
      <span>{{ user.name }}</span>
      <span class="level-badge">{{ user.cefrLevel }}</span>
      <a href="/auth/logout" class="logout-btn">Logout</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="welcome">
      <h1>Tervetuloa, {{ user.name }}!</h1>
      <p>Continue your Finnish learning journey</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">üìö</div>
        <h2>Flashcards</h2>
        <p>Review vocabulary with spaced repetition to build your Finnish word bank effectively.</p>
        <a href="/flashcards" class="card-link">Practice Vocabulary</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">‚úèÔ∏è</div>
        <h2>Verb Conjugation</h2>
        <p>Master Finnish verb types and their conjugation patterns across different tenses.</p>
        <a href="/verbs" class="card-link">Conjugate Verbs</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">üî§</div>
        <h2>Noun Declension</h2>
        <p>Practice the 15 Finnish grammatical cases and learn when to use each one.</p>
        <a href="/nouns" class="card-link">Decline Nouns</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">üìñ</div>
        <h2>Reading Practice</h2>
        <p>Read stories tailored to your CEFR level and expand your comprehension skills.</p>
        <a href="/reading" class="card-link">Read Stories</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">üìù</div>
        <h2>Mock Exams</h2>
        <p>Test your Finnish skills with CEFR-aligned practice exams and track your progress.</p>
        <a href="/exams" class="card-link">Take an Exam</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
